    "title": "Kutoa Kikristo",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "kutoa kikristo",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Kutoa kwa ukarimu kwa Kikristo kunaonyesha neema ya kweli. Tunaona hili katika &quot;Bwana wetu Yesu Kristo, kwamba ingawa Alikuwa tajiri, lakini kwa ajili yenu Alifanyika maskini, ili ninyi kwa umaskini wake mpate kuwa matajiri&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:9\">2 Wakorintho 8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:5-Phil2:8\">Wafilipi 2:5–8</a>). Tumepokea kibali chake kisichostahiliwa katika wokovu, na tunatoa kwa ukarimu kama jibu kwa “zawadi yake isiyoelezeka!” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:15\">2 Wakorintho 9:15</a>).</p><p>Yesu alifundisha kwamba ukarimu unaonyesha ni nani anayemfuata (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:34-Matt25:36\">Mathayo 25:34–36</a>). Alisisitiza umuhimu wa nia na mtazamo wa mtu, siyo tu kiasi kinachotolewa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:41-Mark12:44\">Marko 12:41–44</a>).</p><p>Kwenye 2 Wakorintho, mtume Paulo anasisitiza umuhimu wa kutoa. Anahimiza kanisa la Korintho kutoa kwa ukarimu ili kusaidia wale wenye mahitaji, hasa Wakristo Wayahudi maskini huko Yerusalemu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:6-2Cor8:7\">2 Wakorintho 8:6–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:1-2Cor9:5\">9:1–5</a>). Ukarimu huu ungeonyesha kwamba Wakristo wa Mataifa na Wakristo Wayahudi huko Yerusalemu ni sehemu ya &quot;mwili&quot; mmoja.</p><p>Hapa kuna muhtasari wa mafundisho ya Paulo kuhusu utoaji wa Kikristo:</p><ol><li><p>Kutoa kwetu kunapaswa kutoka kwa nia na moyo wa hiari (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:12\">2 Wakorintho 8:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:7\">9:7</a>). Paulo anasisitiza nia kwa sababu sababu ya kutoa kwetu ni muhimu zaidi.</p></li><li><p>Kutoa kwa moyo wa kweli huleta furaha, tofauti na zawadi zinazotolewa kwa kusitasita (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:5\">2 Wakorintho 9:5</a>). Tunapotoa kwa wengine, tunapata furaha, kama vile mkulima anavyofurahia kupanda mbegu kwa sababu anajua mazao yatakua (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:6-2Cor9:10\">9:6–10</a>). Kushiriki na wale wanaohitaji pia huleta furaha (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:1-2Cor9:2\">9:1–2</a>).</p></li><li><p>Kutoa Kikristo ni tendo la ukarimu na linaweza kuhusisha kujitolea, kama ilivyoonyeshwa na Wamakedonia (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:1-2Cor8:5\">2 Wakorintho 8:1–5</a>).</p></li><li><p>Kushughulikia zawadi za kifedha kunahitaji uaminifu, uadilifu, na uangalifu. Paulo alihakikisha wenzake waliokusanya zawadi kutoka kwa makanisa wanakingwa dhidi ya tuhuma (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:20-2Cor8:21\">2 Wakorintho 8:20–21</a>). Watu wanaosimamia michango ya kanisa wanapaswa kuwa na sifa na uwajibikaji uliohakikishwa.</p></li></ol><p>Maisha ya Kikristo yanapaswa kuonyesha ukarimu kwa wale wenye uhitaji. Paulo anawaagiza Wakristo kumpendeza Mungu, si wao wenyewe (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:15\">2 Wakorintho 5:15</a>). Wakristo wanapaswa kuishi chini ya uongozi wa Yesu, na upendo wake unapaswa kuwachochea (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:14\">5:14</a>). Tunaweza kuonyesha upendo wake waziwazi kupitia utoaji wetu.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:2\">Kutoka 25:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:5\">35:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:35\">Mambo ya Walawi 25:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:7-Deut15:11\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 15:7–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:17\">16:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:9\">1 Mambo ya Nyakati 29:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:9-Prov3:10\">Mithali 3:9–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:24-Prov11:26\">11:24–26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:13\">21:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:27\">28:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:8\">Malaki 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:42\">Mathayo 5:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:3-Matt6:4\">6:3–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:8\">10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:21\">19:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:38\">Luka 6:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:41\">11:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:33-Luke12:34\">12:33–34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:22\">18:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:29\">Matendo 11:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:3\">1 Wakorintho 13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:2-1Cor16:3\">16:2–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:17-2Cor5:18\">2 Wakorintho 5:17–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:1-2Cor9:15\">2 Wakorintho 8:1–9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:3-Phil2:11\">Wafilipi 2:3–11</a></p>",
